{"tid":1794734,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【母愛氾濫】姚樂怡為4歲囡囡賀生日 44歲契媽佘詩曼陪畫花面","createTime":"2019-12-23T10:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T00:39:41.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8f952b6aa7fff4450d230211fe219c807e3bb355","tid":1794734,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T10:45:16.000Z","msg":"姚樂怡和圈外老公吳俊匡結婚7年，育有獨生女Gaibe（乳名小雞髀），為慶祝女兒昨日踏入4歲，姚樂怡幫囡囡搞生日派對，「七魔女」成員佘詩曼和湯盈盈都有出席，身為契媽的阿佘，更在面上畫了雪人公仔彩繪，化身大細路，與「蝴蝶」契女鬥可愛。<br />\n姚樂怡留言祝囡囡生日快樂：「冬至Baby #小雞髀 噚日生日party好開心，多謝好多朋友、契媽佘佘要開工都趕過嚟，Love U All，小雞髀同朋友仔玩超開心，尤其切蛋糕小朋友邊食邊攞糖糖好可愛。」<br />\n湯盈盈帶兩女出席生日會，大女錢凱晴（Alyssa）越大越似老竇錢嘉樂，細女錢凱琪（Kassidy）就好嗲媽咪，不過兩姐妹都沒在面上畫彩繪，不知是否怕醜呢！陳敏之留言祝小雞髀：「Happy Birthday Gaibe 」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191223/large/1577091393_4d61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191223%2Flarge%2F1577091393_4d61.jpg&h=ce3a1008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191223/60409806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191223%2F60409806&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=2c1ef3e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191223%2F60409806&h=5289e0de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191223/60409806</a>"},{"pid":"65098029ccf1b62bedde15e34ac9f1223c55dfa8","tid":1794734,"uid":165339,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T10:47:14.000Z","msg":"連登女兒又搶fo"},{"pid":"7b1b05a3e152fa0f256fefb7bdcf53eb16d189ba","tid":1794734,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T10:48:12.000Z","msg":"錢家基因"},{"pid":"105054c3323347e112a542065f4fa4b71cf1ec9e","tid":1794734,"uid":889